ehmen Kittsteiners Anregungen wieder auf und diskutieren seine von geschichtsphilosophischen Fragestellungen angeleitete Kulturgeschichte neu.  aWhat are the possibilities of a "philosophy of history after the philosophy of history"? Interrogating the work of Heinz Dieter Kittsteiner, the contributions of this volume explore this question.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 4aGeschichtsphilosophie. 4aGeschichtstheorie. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aPhilosophie. 7aHISTORY / Social History.2bisacsh  aCultural History.  aHistory.  aPhilosophy of History.  aPhilosophy.  aTheory of History.1 aBlänkner, Reinhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBlänkner, Reinhard, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aDunkhase, Jan Eike, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFaber, Richard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFreyberg, Sascha, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKittsteiner, Heinz Dieter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKlenner, Jost Philipp, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLandwehr, Achim, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNeuffer, Moritz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRahden, Wolfert von, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmieder, Falko, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmieder, Falko, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aVoller, Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVoller, Christian, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWagner, Jann